{"tid":2275435,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科學創新教育又關「國教」事？楊潤雄：非待於「自己世界」要理解與國家關係","createTime":"2020-11-07T07:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T09:39:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7464b6799a6f4b921cb4b783f98ce70178c65593","tid":2275435,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:04:07.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄今日（7日）出席一個關於科學創新教育研討會演講時表示，未來教育將要順應科技發展趨勢發展，而培養使用者的質素、價值觀同樣重要，他舉例指網上短片有真偽，需教導學童如何辨別網上短片真偽、對錯不應只依靠網上資訊，教育界需思考人文質素培育能否配合科技發展的速度。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄稱，科技快速發展，人工智能推動社會進步，惟其造福與否取決於使用者，因此人文質素及價值觀培養亦需同等重視，並需留意科技發展速度會否較素養培育快。他又提到，科技可因應學生能力不同促使教育個人化是好事，惟同時亦須教育學生群體生活，明白作為社會一分子如何貢獻社會，而非待於「自己世界」，而是現實世界，並學習人與人之間的關係，以及如何理解自己與國家的關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201107/4A3F7NEO7ZDAHO3LHIGVL4KJ7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201107%2F4A3F7NEO7ZDAHO3LHIGVL4KJ7Y%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuF%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=51ab6cc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201107%2F4A3F7NEO7ZDAHO3LHIGVL4KJ7Y%2F&h=39ee85ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201107/4A3F7NEO7ZDAHO3LHIGVL4KJ7Y/</a>"},{"pid":"96aacbbe9feb87f726f93a87fb9911742c131bc0","tid":2275435,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d103ff318cb9d11f628c86fef84e36cc435185","tid":2275435,"uid":305767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大煉芯"},{"pid":"aba9a7a07f2